  "detailed_description": "<br><br>Expedition Zero — survival horror set in the anomaly zone of the northern forest. <br>Face the dreadful forest monster and find a way to defeat it. <br><br>Explore the corrupted forest and abandoned research facilities to uncover the truth about the top-secret expedition. <br>Limited resources can be used to enhance your abilities and chances of survival in extreme conditions. <br>Could you escape the zone or reveal the secrets it keeps? <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1247570/extras/a92181a050079509518d3a9439888fcf.poster.avif?t=1727198856\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1247570/extras/a92181a050079509518d3a9439888fcf.webm?t=1727198856\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1247570/extras/a92181a050079509518d3a9439888fcf.mp4?t=1727198856\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Key Features:<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fight or Hide</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1247570/extras/5112394b20a920c76676b5d745ea42be.poster.avif?t=1727198856\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1247570/extras/5112394b20a920c76676b5d745ea42be.webm?t=1727198856\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1247570/extras/5112394b20a920c76676b5d745ea42be.mp4?t=1727198856\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>You are not alone in the forest. <br>Face the horrifying monster in a deadly duel. <br>How would you deal with other corrupted creatures? <br>Run away, fight back or become prey.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Survive </h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1247570/extras/7f99c09d8736a010de88ac9138e04f69.poster.avif?t=1727198856\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1247570/extras/7f99c09d8736a010de88ac9138e04f69.webm?t=1727198856\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1247570/extras/7f99c09d8736a010de88ac9138e04f69.mp4?t=1727198856\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Deadly monsters are not your only enemy. <br>Deal with lack of resources, extreme temperatures and snowstorms.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Get Strong</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1247570/extras/6cbfb684f366fb12887e6948358ee09f.poster.avif?t=1727198856\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1247570/extras/6cbfb684f366fb12887e6948358ee09f.webm?t=1727198856\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1247570/extras/6cbfb684f366fb12887e6948358ee09f.mp4?t=1727198856\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Loot and craft useful devices and modules for your mecha-suit. <br>Establish new safe points to have uneasy rest. <br>It is the only help you'll get on the expedition.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore The Unknown</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1247570/extras/317c7d530f401c97581e2e6a2c3b29e0.poster.avif?t=1727198856\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1247570/extras/317c7d530f401c97581e2e6a2c3b29e0.webm?t=1727198856\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1247570/extras/317c7d530f401c97581e2e6a2c3b29e0.mp4?t=1727198856\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The former research camp is now abandoned and surrounded by a 50m high wall. <br>Uncover the dark truth about the research expedition and top-secret experiment.",
  "about_the_game": "<br><br>Expedition Zero — survival horror set in the anomaly zone of the northern forest. <br>Face the dreadful forest monster and find a way to defeat it. <br><br>Explore the corrupted forest and abandoned research facilities to uncover the truth about the top-secret expedition. <br>Limited resources can be used to enhance your abilities and chances of survival in extreme conditions. <br>Could you escape the zone or reveal the secrets it keeps? <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1247570/extras/a92181a050079509518d3a9439888fcf.poster.avif?t=1727198856\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1247570/extras/a92181a050079509518d3a9439888fcf.webm?t=1727198856\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1247570/extras/a92181a050079509518d3a9439888fcf.mp4?t=1727198856\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Key Features:<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fight or Hide</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1247570/extras/5112394b20a920c76676b5d745ea42be.poster.avif?t=1727198856\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1247570/extras/5112394b20a920c76676b5d745ea42be.webm?t=1727198856\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1247570/extras/5112394b20a920c76676b5d745ea42be.mp4?t=1727198856\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>You are not alone in the forest. <br>Face the horrifying monster in a deadly duel. <br>How would you deal with other corrupted creatures? <br>Run away, fight back or become prey.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Survive </h2><span